Do you want to buy a brand-new, architect-designed, modern, trendy property in a well-established northern upmarket neighbourhood? Mount Sophia is set in the northern hills of Bloemfontein and epitomises country living within an urban environment. It comprises 56 units in an environmentally friendly, low-maintenance complex offering a tasteful range of choices extending from two to four bedroom homes. Prices range from R1 100 000 to R2 300 000. This complex is ready for occupation, with units in Phase 1 and 2 featuring the high standards and finishes that Lenova is noted for. Call 076-391-4068 or send email to marketing@ lenovaconstruction.co.za.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.